{"tid":2225744,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港人係唔係慣左free ride？","createTime":"2020-10-01T14:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T10:59:28.000Z","uid":247211,"like":55,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7d005bbfe3c4a1777640cb1bb9f23a58a1ded5e9","tid":2225744,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:02:54.000Z","msg":"free ride呢個習慣由細開始建立<br />\n中學做功課借人地既抄<br />\n大學做gp project交俾group mate<br />\n出黎做野靠同事靠擦鞋<br />\n<br />\n到依家追求民主自由又係靠班靚仔<br />\n個個都口講到自己好黃<br />\n但肯付出自己前途自由去爭取既又有幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都只係想享受自由<br />\n要付出要去犧牲爭取自由既時候個個就想free ride<br />\n<br />\n睇住71之後每次越黎越少人出<br />\n一息尚存抗爭到底呢句口號<br />\n其實係咪淨係適用於少部份人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人係咪free ride慣連民主自由都要free ride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d550859ab05612bdc89ecb8ba35d75b107ec634","tid":2225744,"uid":231583,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3b7d3fe4bc30b0f1ecf0d9a5e34e619a4571040","tid":2225744,"uid":103833,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"香港人生性自私唔係新聞嚟㗎啦 其實同大陸人一樣都係低等物種<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講啦 睇緊英國樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdad53d386a5f20b97cef2414c854d6083aedc23","tid":2225744,"uid":375645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"人嘅天性嚟，只能夠講香港冇人做到領導者帶領大家"},{"pid":"d5d6a7881c869990324815c9df5b45512afbf0b6","tid":2225744,"uid":263349,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"可以去英國 唔洗抗爭lu"},{"pid":"e63f67c684e5430b94d8b54f0996d2186fd2397b","tid":2225744,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"由抗爭到戰爭，由覺醒到破局需要嘅心態。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2219689\" data-auto-link target=\"_