者話能力)真係只容許佢地淺層參與，只理過係執權者將參與嘅成本同標準愈推愈高先會有少左人出聲嘅現象<br />\n<br />\n而家行出街一個唔好彩無理由就拉入狗屋<br />\n同上年帶哂gear俾狗拉入狗屋差唔多<br />\n如果呢班人承受到呢個風險<br />\n咁都可以合理推斷上年行出街九成人都有gear喺身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n執權者就係想做到咁令異見者睇落少左<br />\n我地無力阻止佢拉高標準都唔係傻到幫佢地手吹個咁嘅風向啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0383d1609cca91b7d4aa0cd8d68b8864b72c56d","tid":2225744,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93361e95dc2d254886bb6c9edddd4d5f7628772f","tid":2225744,"uid":105691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不自由 毋寧死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人 報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今生只嫁前線巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好撚鐘意香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足不是condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要食多d黃店幫手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji